---
const profileImage = '/Isaac_perfil.jpg';
---

<section class="about section" id="about">
  <div class="about__media">
    <div class="avatar" aria-hidden="true">
      <img src={profileImage} alt="Foto de perfil de Sergio Isaac Moreno Alvarez" loading="eager" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about__content">
    <p class="section__label">Sobre mí</p>
    <h2>Aprendo rápido, cuido los detalles y disfruto construir bases limpias.</h2>
    <p>
      Me estoy formando como desarrollador frontend con foco en HTML, CSS, JavaScript y Astro. Busco proyectos donde pueda aportar criterio visual, consistencia y ganas de mejorar cada entrega.
    </p>

    <div class="availability">
      <span class="availability__dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span>Disponible para proyectos</span>
    </div>

    <div class="stats" aria-label="Estadísticas de perfil">
      <article>
        <strong>06</strong>
        <span>proyectos</span>
      </article>
      <article>
        <strong>08</strong>
        <span>meses de experiencia</span>
      </article>
      <article>
        <strong>100%</strong>
        <span>dedicación</span>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section {
    max-width: 1160px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem clamp(1rem, 3vw, 2rem);
  }

  .about {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about__media {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
  }

  .avatar {
    position: relative;
    width: min(72vw, 18rem);
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--foam) 24%, transparent), transparent 35%), color-mix(in srgb, var(--roast) 84%, transparent);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .avatar::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: -0.7rem;
    border: 2px dotted color-mix(in srgb, var(--foam) 80%, transparent);
    border-radius: inherit;
    animation: spin 12s linear infinite;
  }

  .avatar img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 18%;
    border-radius: inherit;
    filter: saturate(0.94) contrast(1.04);
  }

  .about__content {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .section__label {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--foam);
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    line-height: 1;
    max-width: 14ch;
  }

  p {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 62ch;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .availability {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    width: fit-content;
    padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--roast) 82%, transparent);
    color: var(--cream);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .availability__dot {
    width: 0.75rem;
    height: 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #4ade80;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 color-mix(in srgb, #4ade80 60%, transparent);
    animation: pulse 1.8s infinite;
  }

  .stats {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stats article {
    padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--roast) 88%, transparent);
  }

  .stats strong {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.2rem);
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    color: var(--caramel);
  }

  .stats span {
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  @keyframes spin {
    to {
      transform: rotate(360deg);
    }
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%,
    100% {
      transform: scale(1);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 color-mix(in srgb, #4ade80 58%, transparent);
    }

    50% {
      transform: scale(1.08);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.45rem color-mix(in srgb, #4ade80 0%, transparent);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 800px) {
    .about {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(260px, 0.9fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .stats {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }
</style>
